skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: john's wall
des: Intended for users in Ann Arbor, MI but accessible to users across the globe, anyone can use this skill to contribute to an evolving art project where anyone can post anything they want and it will appear on a decorative and entertaining wallboard in Ann Arbor. Your message will remain on the wallboard until it is replaced by another user.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
